            <h5>Software Engineer, Kuali</h5>
            <p>Aimee Knight is a figure skater turned software engineer, proud wife of an Iraq and Afghanistan veteran, and a panelist on the
            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/javascript-jabber/id496893300?mt=2">JavaScript Jabber podcast</a>. Mrs. Knight graduated from the <a href="http://nashvillesoftwareschool.com">Nashville Software School (NSS)</a> in 2014, and now works at <a href="https://www.kuali.co">Kuali.co</a> helping build open source software for higher education using React.js and Node.</p>
