            <span class="card-title">David Molina (<a href="https://twitter.com/davidcmolina">@davidcmolina</a>)</span>
            <h5>Founder/Executive Director, Operation Code</h5>
            <p>David Molina is the Founder/Executive Director of Operation Code, an open source project he started on August 21, 2014 when he wrote the first line of code to <a href="https://github.com/OperationCode/operationcode">GitHub</a>. Mr. Molina is a ex-Army Captain, and currently resides in Portland, Oregon with his wife and three young daughters. <a href="/founder">Read his story.</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
